  },
  {
    "_id": "e39cf9e5-1bf8-455c-b1b3-50d21662ce12",
    "companyName": "Label A",
    "contractName": null,
    "description": [
      {
        "_key": "c89afdc4a0d3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "beb8a2f871a3",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "After a few years in game development I missed the faster pace of web work, so I returned to Label A. When I first interned there it was a three-person startup. By the time I came back it had grown to over 20 people across two offices. I worked on a wide range of applications, from small widgets to full platforms:"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "c7b2fcec56b2",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "bae00d0bd5cf",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": ["strong"],
            "text": "WoW KNMI"
          },
          {
            "_key": "5754ee6f5fa7",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\nA map showing user measurement stations where visitors can compare stations and view detailed data. (This was actually my first introduction to KNMI, years before I'd join them full-time.)"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "a166647396a4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "040e283e42a1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": ["strong"],
            "text": "RIVM"
          },
          {
            "_key": "8a45c33cfe1a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\nA map displaying real-time air quality measurements across the Netherlands."
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "97bad251ad97",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "9f3bc6cd0a0f",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": ["strong"],
            "text": "Taxi Electric"
          },
          {
            "_key": "2fe4189275e1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\nFor a new electric taxi company, we developed an application that allowed users to book a taxi. Administrators could track taxi locations, monitor their remaining range, and schedule ride; all in real time."
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "77872f2056c4",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "cba0a553b78e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": ["strong"],
            "text": "Veilig Verkeer Nederland (Safe Traffic Netherlands)"
          },
          {
            "_key": "d5106f1e00ec",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "\nAn application that let users report unsafe traffic situations on a map. We used "
          },
          {
            "_key": "fe36c359ccd6",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": ["6f5d74b3b983"],
            "text": "GeoServer"
          },
          {
            "_key": "afd7cc09d83a",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " to keep map performance smooth at scale."
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "6f5d74b3b983",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "/tags/geoserver"
          }
        ],
        "style": "normal"
      }
    ],
