            "_key": "f8007fde2a65",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "During my studies, a group of us built a serious game in the Games & Simulations minor where players gained in-game advantages by saving electricity at home. After graduation, the company hired me to finish it."
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "fd13511a2dae",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "72258e9de444",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "We originally used Unity, but with a much smaller team than we'd had as students, we needed to compromise. We switched to 2D and moved to Flash to save development time. In the end we shipped a working game that connected to real smart meters."
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
